</%args>

% unless ($isbn) {
<h2>Books</h2>

Books commonly recommended on the beginners lists. If a book isn't
mentioned in this list it might still be good, but there is a good
chance it isn't.  :-)

% }

% for my $b (@books) {
%   next if $isbn and $isbn ne $b->{isbn};
